title: Love Live! - Wake Me Up Before You Go (Doujinshi)
description: Author’s pixiv comment: This is a two year-old book released at the NozoEli-only event “Sweet Sweet Sweet” held on February 21st, 2016. I’m not planning on reprints, so I’m releasing it. To everyone who bought it at the time, thank you so much. I can’t believe it’s been two years already…this is a story about Nozomi who wants to be woken.
